definitions.text:
@khô héo
* verb
- to fade; to wilt; to wither

@khô kháo
- Dry
=Đường khô ráo rồi rất dễ đi+The roads are dry and very passable

@khô mực
* noun
-dried cuttlefish

@khô cạn
- Dried up, affectedby drought
=Hạn hán mấy tuần các cánh đồng đều khô cạn+The fields were dry after many weeks of drought

@khô khan
- Dry
=Bài văn khô khan+A dry literary composition
